channel.title: My NO-IP keeps changing
channel.description: My server is randomly going down and when i go to my No-Ip it says the ip is 192.168.1.3... when it needs to be the other one... when i switch it, it auto changes back to 192.168.1.3 in about 30 minutes. What do i do to lock it?
